breaking_speed.property_description:
If the tool has efficiency, then you get an additional (1+level^2) when using the proper tool
If you have haste, then your mining speed increases by (20*level)% per level of Haste
If the player is not on ground, or if the player's head is under water and not using aqua affinity, then additional 5x penalties are added.
Obtained from the wiki. For further information, see: https://minecraft.wiki/w/Breaking#Speed
